                        Next we need to decide on a Contact page. Contact pages are useful for givin your viewers one or more methods of contacting you for questions or comments. The standard
                        Account only allows for basic information to be display in one element, however premium users can get more features added to this page. Would you like a contact page?
                    </p>
                </div>
